<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>PAWSH Section</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="stylesheets/style.css">
  <style>
    body {
    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    background: #f9f9f9;
    color: #333;
    }

    .pawsh-hero {
    background: #e53935;
    color: white;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    .pawsh-hero .logo {
    max-width: 400px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .pawsh-hero h1 {
    font-size: 28px;
    margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .pawsh-hero p {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 10px auto;
    line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .pawsh-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 20px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    .pawsh-links .link-item {
    text-align: center;
    flex: 1 1 200px;
    max-width: 300px;
    }

    .pawsh-links img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .pawsh-links h3 {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 16px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .pawsh-feature {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    gap: 20px;
    }

    .feature-text {
    flex: 1 1 300px;
    }

    .feature-text h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    }

    .feature-text a {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 10px;
    color: #e53935;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    }

    .feature-image {
    flex: 1 1 300px;
    }

    .feature-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="container header-container">
        <a href="/"><div class="logo">PAWSH</div></a>
        <nav class="main-nav">
            <a href="/">Home</a>
            <a href="/ourstory">Our Story</a>
            <a href="/shop">Shop</a>
            <a href="/contact">Contact Us</a>
        </nav>
        <div class="profile-icon">
             <a href="/profile"><img src="img/user.png" alt="Profile"></a>
        </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section class="pawsh-hero">
        <img src="img/pet.webp" alt="Pet #1" class="logo" />
        <h1>ANYTHING for PETS</h1>
        <p>
        We love pets, and we believe loving pets makes us better people. That’s one of the many reasons we do Anything for Pets – because they will do anything for us. Anything for Pets is our commitment to pet parents; it’s how we do business and who we are as pet lovers. As the leader in pet care, we make our decisions based on how we can bring pet parents closer to their pets.
        </p>
        <p>
        From dressing in matching costumes, to finding the perfect treats and toys, we innovate solutions and unique, must-have products to create more ways for pets to be a part of our everyday lives.
        </p>
        <p>
        Our trusted and skilled associates share the same passion for pets as the pet parents we serve, helping pet parents choose from our offering of the largest variety of pet products and services in one convenient place – in your neighborhood or the palm of your hand. With more than 9,999 locations in North America, we pride ourselves on our unrivaled variety of pet food, treats, toys, and apparel, as well as our services including training, grooming, boarding and more.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="pawsh-feature">
        <div class="feature-text">
        <h2>10 Reasons to Love #LifeAtPawsh</h2>
        <p>
            Since 2025, we’ve committed over $999.99 million to increased wages and benefits to help ensure the health, safety, and well-being of associates. We want them to come to pawsh because they love pets, and we want them to stay because of our culture, opportunities for belonging and growth, and in building a future for themselves here. Here are 10 great reasons why #LifeAtpawsh is so doggone great!
        </p>
        <a href="/shop">Continue Shopping &rarr;</a>
        </div>
        <div class="feature-image">
            <img src="img/pet2.webp" alt="Pet #2 " class="logo" />
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>